message.text:
𝐋𝐞𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐮𝐩 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐠𝐚𝐦𝐞 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐈𝐀𝐒𝐂-𝐅𝐄𝐔! 💚💙

Think you’ve got what it takes to shine on the court or dominate online? Now’s your chance to represent us in basketball, volleyball, table tennis, badminton, chess, and E-Sports!

The Institute of Internal Auditors Student Chapter-FEU is opening its doors to students who are ready to rise, compete, and leave a mark. Be part of a community that celebrates sportsmanship as much as success. Let’s set new standards together in the Athlete Search 2025!

Registration is now open until the maximum slots are filled.

ATHLETE SEARCH REGISTRATION FORM
 📌 https://bit.ly/AthleteSearch2025RegistrationForm

Step into the arena with Integrity, aim for Excellence, and let the colors Blue and Green shine in every rally, shot, checkmate, and clutch play!

For further inquiries, kindly reach out:
Elgar James Caharian - Vice President

#IAbante

Caption by Elgar James Caharian
Pubmat by Samantha Mascariñas and Elgar James Caharian

message.text:
𝐋𝐞𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐮𝐩 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐠𝐚𝐦𝐞 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐈𝐀𝐒𝐂-𝐅𝐄𝐔! 💚💙

Think you’ve got what it takes to shine on the court or dominate online? Now’s your chance to represent us in basketball, volleyball, table tennis, badminton, chess, and E-Sports!

The Institute of Internal Auditors Student Chapter-FEU is opening its doors to students who are ready to rise, compete, and leave a mark. Be part of a community that celebrates sportsmanship as much as success. Let’s set new standards together in the Athlete Search 2025!

Registration is now open until the maximum slots are filled.

ATHLETE SEARCH REGISTRATION FORM
 📌 https://bit.ly/AthleteSearch2025RegistrationForm

Step into the arena with Integrity, aim for Excellence, and let the colors Blue and Green shine in every rally, shot, checkmate, and clutch play!

For further inquiries, kindly reach out:
Elgar James Caharian - Vice President

#IAbante

Caption by Elgar James Caharian
Pubmat by Samantha Mascariñas and Elgar James Caharian

𝐋𝐞𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐮𝐩 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐠𝐚𝐦𝐞 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐈𝐀𝐒𝐂-𝐅𝐄𝐔! 💚💙

Think you’ve got what it takes to shine on the court or dominate online? Now’s your chance to represent us in basketball, volleyball, table tennis, badminton, chess, and E-Sports!

The Institute of Internal Auditors Student Chapter-FEU is opening its doors to students who are ready to rise, compete, and leave a mark. Be part of a community that celebrates sportsmanship as much as success. Let’s set new standards together in the Athlete Search 2025!

Registration is now open until the maximum slots are filled.

ATHLETE SEARCH REGISTRATION FORM
 📌 https://bit.ly/AthleteSearch2025RegistrationForm

Step into the arena with Integrity, aim for Excellence, and let the colors Blue and Green shine in every rally, shot, checkmate, and clutch play!

For further inquiries, kindly reach out:
Elgar James Caharian - Vice President
